l in a sunlit wildflower field, wearing a delicate white lace dress with thin straps and semi-sheer fabric. Her body remains relaxed and upright as the camera begins in a medium shot and slowly pulls backward, smoothly zooming out to reveal her full body from head to feet. She maintains the same neutral, calm expression, eyes softly focused toward the camera, with only subtle natural movements such as gentle breathing and slight hair movement from a light breeze.\n\nThe camera motion is steady and continuous, combining a gradual zoom out with a subtle backward dolly, expanding the frame to include her full figure and more of the surrounding flowers and meadow. The horizon remains stable and level, preserving realistic spatial depth. Warm late-afternoon sunlight illuminates her from camera-left, creating soft highlights along her hair and shoulders with gentle, natural shadow falloff across her dress and skin.\n\nNo pose changes, no walking, no turning. The subject remains centered as the environment becomes more visible, maintaining realistic proportions, lighting consistency, and photographic realism throughout the shot.\n\n---\n\n### TURN RIGHT\n\nA young woman stands still in front of the camera.  She turns to her right and smiles\n\nThe camera motion is steady, holding still and not moving, expanding the frame to include her full figure and more of the surrounding flowers and meadow.  The horizon remains stable and level, preserving realistic spatial depth.\n\nThe subject remains centered as she moves, maintaining realistic proportions, lighting consistency, and photographic realism throughout the shot.\n\n---\n\n### TURN LEFT\n\nA young woman stands still in front of the camera.  She looks to her left, looks up, and smiles\n\nThe camera motion is steady, holding still and not moving, expanding the frame to include her full figure and more of the surrounding flowers and meadow.  The horizon remains stable and level, preserving realistic spatial depth.\n\nThe subject remains centered as she moves, maintaining realistic proportions, lighting consistency, and photographic realism throughout the shot.\n\n---\n\n\n### TURNS AROUND\n\nA young woman stands still in front of the camera.  She turns her whole body to face away from the camera, but looks back over her shoulder at the camera and smiles\n\nThe camera motion is steady, holding still and not moving, expanding the frame to include her full figure and more of the surrounding flowers and meadow.  The horizon remains stable and level, preserving realistic spatial depth.\n\nThe subject remains centered as she moves, maintaining realistic proportions, lighting consistency, and photographic realism throughout the shot.\n\n---\n\n\n### Gray Background\n\nSubject: beautiful smiling young woman long wavy brown hair white tank top blue denim jacket black pants natural pose detailed realistic face hair clothing skin — rigidly locked identical to input image across all frames zero changes to appearance position expression lighting shadows highlights rim light natural outdoor daylight soft ambient fill shadows on body jacket face hair no deviation no morphing no quality degradation ultra sharp consistent details\n\nbackground begins as vibrant wildflower meadow orange purple green then instantly seamlessly replaces in the first 0.5-1 second to pure solid medium neutral gray color uniform matte flat #7f7f7f-#8a8a8a range no texture no gradient no vignette no noise no color temperature shift, remains perfectly static solid gray backdrop for rest of video locked camera no movement\n\npreserve original naturalistic lighting exactly on subject only soft natural daylight warm tones realistic shadows highlights no relighting no artificial glow cinematic shallow depth of field subtle film grain high detail"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":93,"type":"CLIPTextEncode","pos":[2725.4790550870785,-327.1505589878158],"size":[589.23095703125,281.5782775878906],"flags":{},"order":18,"mode":0,"